STOSSEL - [The Republican Debate - Live] - Fox Business Network
2011, August 11, Thursday

Xvid/MP3 AVI - ripped from EdgarS789's .flv file.

[from John Stossel's blog:]

Tonight I have a two hour show - we'll be on during and after the Republican presidential candidates' debate.

Steve Forbes, Reason's Matt Welch, columnist Deroy Murdock, Nikki Neily of the Independent Women's Forum, a live studio audience and I plan to offer a different take on the debate - a libertarian take - that you won't see anywhere else.

Tonight at 10 PM (ET) on the Fox Business Network.
